      • configure

        public void configure()
        Configure the conditions system before it is initialized.

        An SVT specific setup class is added to the manager here.

        This method will also optionally setup the org.hps.run.database.RunManager and can pass a set of tags to the conditions manager.

        Specified by:
        configure in interface ConditionsSetup
        Overrides:
        configure in class DefaultConditionsSetup

      • postInitialize

        public void postInitialize()
        Do post initialization of conditions system, which will freeze the manager if it is already fully initialized, meaning that the detector name and run were given as arguments which will override the information from the event header in the data.
        Specified by:
        postInitialize in interface ConditionsSetup
        Overrides:
        postInitialize in class DefaultConditionsSetup

        Do cleanup of conditions system after job.
